{"tid":313294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無唇炎患者？","createTime":"2017-07-08T08:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T14:43:31.000Z","uid":95075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d454bfa4185e2416b52179b45afb06f47ea47d18","tid":313294,"uid":95075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"兩個月前嘴唇無啦啦刺痛<br />\n第二日已經腫哂同埋起啲唔痛既粒粒水泡<br />\n睇完醫生食完抗生素叫做好番<br />\n但乾到仆街 個醫生又無開潤唇膏<br />\n結果一用番潤唇膏就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個星期又番發 嚴重到流哂黃水結哂痂<br />\n食左成個月抗生素終於好轉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都仲係好乾同埋唇邊仲有紅印<br />\n完全唔知可以點預防同斷尾<br />\n可以戒既野都戒哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a1239d9e88c1d6ae4c37f30d9f55fde8658640","tid":313294,"uid":46889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"我都有唇炎，宜家要keep住用make up for ever 支唇膏先舒緩到，都兩三年。枝唇膏唔平，每個月一次"},{"pid":"78b9b0550201f98fc5c77fab4d744c4f88c11200","tid":313294,"uid":46566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"有啊,我係個下唇會腫同有白膜,睇左2個月中醫都未好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8894804230bf0a14bf71877d9e1fd189d7336d6","tid":313294,"uid":46566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fc14338df7a0421fc633698ac3db4fdc929349","tid":313294,"uid":143540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9707dc5786a892aa98afaa9950e0f461e336c0","tid":313294,"uid":143540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:23:47.000Z","msg":"樓主而家點？相同問題<br />\n<br />\ntg: jw1227"},{"pid":"81982f30594a63a3d679c981f952e245b2370492","tid":313294,"uid":95075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:43:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主而家點？相同問題<br />\n<br />\ntg: jw1227</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而加好番好多！控制得住，兩個月前的起心肝連少少類固醇都唔用，開頭佢準備好似平常咁番發，過左兩日竟然慢慢退，而加可以完全唔用類固醇！但個嘴長期要搽好厚既潤唇膏，如果唔係就會好乾好乾。"}]}